### ZinTrust – Containers Proxy (Cloudflare + Docker Compose)
### Requires VS Code extension: "REST Client" (humao.rest-client)
###
### Tests both runtimes so you can compare responses side-by-side:
###
###   Cloudflare Containers (wrangler dev)
###     npm run dev:cp
###
###   Docker Compose gateway
###     zin cp up  (gateway exposed on :8800 by default)
###
### All path prefixes are the same in both runtimes:
###   /health          → gateway self
###   /mysql/health    → proxy-mysql
###   /postgres/health → proxy-pg
###   /redis/health    → proxy-redis
###   /mongodb/health  → proxy-mongodb
###   /sqlserver/health→ proxy-sqlserver
###   /smtp/health     → proxy-smtp

# ─── Base URLs ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
@cfBase   = http://localhost:8787
@dcBase   = http://localhost:8800

# Signing credentials (must match APP_KEY / *_PROXY_KEY_ID / *_PROXY_SECRET in .dev.vars)
@keyId    = dev-key
@proxySignature = dev-sig

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# CLOUDFLARE CONTAINERS (wrangler dev)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### [CF] Gateway health
GET {{cfBase}}/health

###

### [CF] MySQL proxy health
GET {{cfBase}}/mysql/health

###

### [CF] PostgreSQL proxy health
GET {{cfBase}}/postgres/health

###

### [CF] Redis proxy health
GET {{cfBase}}/redis/health

###

### [CF] MongoDB proxy health
GET {{cfBase}}/mongodb/health

###

### [CF] SQL Server proxy health
GET {{cfBase}}/sqlserver/health

###

### [CF] SMTP proxy health
GET {{cfBase}}/smtp/health

###

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# DOCKER COMPOSE GATEWAY (zin cp up)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### [DC] Gateway health
GET {{dcBase}}/health

###

### [DC] MySQL proxy health
GET {{dcBase}}/mysql/health

###

### [DC] PostgreSQL proxy health
GET {{dcBase}}/postgres/health

###

### [DC] Redis proxy health
GET {{dcBase}}/redis/health

###

### [DC] MongoDB proxy health
GET {{dcBase}}/mongodb/health

###

### [DC] SQL Server proxy health
GET {{dcBase}}/sqlserver/health

###

### [DC] SMTP proxy health
GET {{dcBase}}/smtp/health

###

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# FUNCTIONAL – MySQL query (via Docker Compose gateway)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### [DC] MySQL – SELECT 1
POST {{dcBase}}/mysql/query
Content-Type: application/json
X-Proxy-Key-Id: {{keyId}}
X-Proxy-Signature: {{proxySignature}}

{
  "sql": "SELECT 1 AS ok"
}

###

### [DC] MySQL – list tables
POST {{dcBase}}/mysql/query
Content-Type: application/json
X-Proxy-Key-Id: {{keyId}}
X-Proxy-Signature: {{proxySignature}}

{
  "sql": "SHOW TABLES"
}

###

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# FUNCTIONAL – PostgreSQL query (via Docker Compose gateway)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### [DC] Postgres – SELECT 1
POST {{dcBase}}/postgres/query
Content-Type: application/json
X-Proxy-Key-Id: {{keyId}}
X-Proxy-Signature: {{proxySignature}}

{
  "sql": "SELECT 1 AS ok"
}

###

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# FUNCTIONAL – Redis (via Docker Compose gateway)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### [DC] Redis – PING
POST {{dcBase}}/redis/command
Content-Type: application/json
X-Proxy-Key-Id: {{keyId}}
X-Proxy-Signature: {{proxySignature}}

{
  "command": "PING"
}

###

### [DC] Redis – SET + GET
POST {{dcBase}}/redis/command
Content-Type: application/json
X-Proxy-Key-Id: {{keyId}}
X-Proxy-Signature: {{proxySignature}}

{
  "command": "SET",
  "args": ["zintrust:test", "hello-from-proxy", "EX", 60]
}

###

POST {{dcBase}}/redis/command
Content-Type: application/json
X-Proxy-Key-Id: {{keyId}}
X-Proxy-Signature: {{proxySignature}}

{
  "command": "GET",
  "args": ["zintrust:test"]
}

###
